		<content:encoded><![CDATA[Elite CareFinders, I highly recommend this agency to all health care providers. My experience with Mrs. Rose, she help me from the start to finish, and beyond. She is very compassionate and her dedication to help our Kupuna and providers / caregiver like my self. In terms of placing our Kupuna, she treat them as her own family. She make sure anything and everything that needs to be done is all meet. She is very approachable and understanding. If you have an open bed, or looking for a placement for your love ones or our Kupuna, pls. I highly recommend Rose at Elite CareFinders. You will find a place called home.
Care Provider.]]></content:encoded>
